<div class="title">True Purpose is Love</div>
<div class="substance">Meditation, 5-MeO-DMT & Cannabis</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=blinded+seer&Exact=1">blinded seer</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; blinded seer. "True Purpose is Love: An Experience with Meditation, 5-MeO-DMT & Cannabis (exp37444)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Oct 20, 2004. erowid.org/exp/37444</div>

<br/>



